Key Match Events: Mitchell Starc pinned Harry Brook lbw with a brilliant delivery
Aaron Hardie claimed two wickets in two balls
Post-Match Reflections: Mitchell Starc made a dramatic entrance to the ODI series with a searing inswinging yorker
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia were bowled out with more than five overs remaining, having been nine-down in the 37th over
Others: Jamie Smith and Jacob Bethell stopped the bleeding with a stand of 55
Adil Rashid claimed his 200th ODI wicket when he removed Glenn Maxwell
